A great experience! The theater has comfortable leather seats with plenty of elbow room. The lobby is modern and inviting featuring a bar and lounge seating. It isn't necessarily cheap however with a Groupon its definitely a great value. The food as tasty especially considering its a theater and not a restaurant. I would definitely recommend this to anyone who enjoys watching a good movie in comfort with a beer and a burger on hand!

